### Additional Open Source & Learner Terms (Outskill Context)

This dashboard repository is created as a completely free, open-source educational resource for software engineers, developers, and learners participating in the **AI Catalyst C2 deep dive into Antigravity**.

* **No Royalties**: You are free to copy, modify, merge, publish, distribute, sublicense, and sell this software or assets derived from it.
* **Commercial & Private Use**: You can use this blueprint in commercial products, startup templates, learning sandboxes, or private portfolios without paying royalties or licensing fees.
* **Attribution**: While not legally required under the MIT License, developers are encouraged to keep a link back to this original learning resource to help other developers find these study materials.
